---
title: Data Demo
notes: This example demonstrates the use of `data` from the library for building data-driven layouts.
layout: demo
---

<h1>{{title}}</h1>

<p>Some examples of using sample JSON and YAML data from the library, as well as using Chance.js to generate data on the fly.</p>

<p>Data below courtesy of <a href="http://www.radfaces.com">Rad Faces</a>.</p>
<ul class="flexbox list--reset" style="flex-wrap: wrap">
  {{#each (data "radfaces")}}
    <li class="u-size6of24">
      <img src="{{image}}">
      <p>{{first_name}} {{last_name}} from {{location}}</p>
    </li>
  {{/each}}
</ul>

<table class="u-size-full">
  <thead>
  <tr>
  <th>Name</th>
      <th>Date</th>
      <th>Description</th>
  </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
    {{#iterate 12}}
  		<tr>
  			<td>{{random "name"}}</td>
  			<td>{{random "date" string=true}}</td>
  			<td>{{random "sentence"}}</td>
  		</tr>
    {{/iterate}}
  </tbody>
</table>

{{#each (data "articles")}}
  <article>
    <header>
      <h2>{{title}}</h2>
      <p>Published by {{author}} on <time pubdate="pubdate">{{timestamp date format="MMM Do, YYYY"}}</time></p>
    </header>
    {{{body}}}
  </article>
{{/each}}
